name: LIKE MIKE '88 ALL-STAR ALLEY-OOP"
description:
The '88 Alley Oop... 

This was Mike's 40th point of the 1988 All-Star Game in the old Chicago Stadium, a half court alley oop from Isiah Thomas to wrap up an amazing weekend of basketball as MJ defends his slam dunk title for back to back slam dunk championships and then drops 40 points in front of the home crowd in route to his first All-Star MVP in only 3 short years in the league.
